headline: F5 price target raised to $345 from $325 at RBC Capital
summary: RBC Capital analyst Matthew Hedberg raised the firm’s price target on F5 (FFIV) to $345 from $325 and keeps an Outperform rating on the shares. The company delivered a strong beat and raise quarter as the October 2025 security incident had minimal impact on results, the analyst tells investors in a research note.
